Package: microweight
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Weighting Microdata Files
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person("Don", "Boyd", , "donboyd5@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Don Boyd <donboyd5@gmail.com>
Description: Tools for splitting record weights for a microdata file across states or 
    other geographies in a manner that hits or comes close to targets for those geographies, 
    for reweighting microdata files, and for other weighting tasks.
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
